org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.handler

Class HBaseGraphHeadHandler<G extends EPGMGraphHead>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.handler.HBaseElementHandler
      • org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.handler.HBaseGraphHeadHandler<G>
  • Type Parameters:
    G - EPGM graph head type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ElementHandler, GraphHeadHandler<G>

    public class HBaseGraphHeadHandler<G extends EPGMGraphHead>
extends HBaseElementHandler
implements GraphHeadHandler<G>
    Used to read/write EPGM graph data from/to a HBase table. Graph data in HBase: |---------|-------------|----------|-----------|-----------| | row-key | meta | data | vertices | edges | |---------|-------------|----------|----- -----|-----------| | "0" | label | k1 | k2 | 0 | 1 | 4 | 0 | 1 | 6 | | |-------------|----------|-----------|---|---|---| | | "Community" | v1 | v2 | | | | | | | |---------|-------------|----------|-----------|---|---|---|
    See Also:
